{
  "id": "adv_card_yu_15_03",
  "title": "鈴村優",
  "script": [
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 0.0533353488
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": null,
      "speakerName": "",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "――お笑い番組収録当日",
      "startTime": 0.8,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_15_03/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_15_03-yu001.m4a",
      "text": "……ついに、この日が来ました\n{user}さん、うちは準備万端です",
      "startTime": 5.8424418886,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 9.4666668416
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_15_03/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_15_03-yu002.m4a",
      "text": "どの角度からでも、どんな難題でも\n全てにボケ倒してみせます！",
      "startTime": 12.7333335083,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 15.1666668416
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_15_03/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_15_03-koh001.m4a",
      "text": "あぁ、優なら出来る。優なら大丈夫だ！\n特訓の最後に、俺を笑いで床に沈めた優なら",
      "startTime": 19.0666668416,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 23.3333335083
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_15_03/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_15_03-yu003.m4a",
      "text": "全然爆笑してくれへん{user}さんが\n初めてお腹を抱えてうずくまった、あの時……",
      "startTime": 26.4333335083,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 32.9913753849
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_15_03/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_15_03-yu004.m4a",
      "text": "うちはお笑いの真髄を掴んだ\n――そう確信しました",
      "startTime": 33.7000001749,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_15_03/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_15_03-koh002.m4a",
      "text": "（優はあの日から、ミュージカルとお笑い）\n（両方の猛練習を重ねてきた）",
      "startTime": 38.5666668416,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 41.3000001749
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_15_03/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_15_03-koh003.m4a",
      "text": "（今の優は、ボケるためだけに存在する戦士だ）\n（顔つきもいつもと違う。これは、もしかすると……）",
      "startTime": 45.2666668416,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_15_03/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_15_03-yu005.m4a",
      "text": "そろそろ時間です\n行ってきます、{user}さん",
      "startTime": 52.0333335083,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 54.5333319824
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_15_03/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_15_03-yu006.m4a",
      "text": "『ホットドッグさん』や『浪速おもしろ剛速球』さんに\n勝って……優勝してきます！",
      "startTime": 57.5333335083,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": null,
      "speakerName": "",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "――お笑い番組収録、中盤",
      "startTime": 61.5666668416,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_pen-01.m4a",
          "delay": 7733.333158400001,
          "startTime": 69.3
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_talkstudio-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "talkstudio-00-noon",
      "startTime": 62.9999983948
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_talkstudio-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "talkstudio-00-noon",
      "startTime": 62.9999983948
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_talkstudio-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "talkstudio-00-noon",
      "startTime": 69.0333350342
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_15_03/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_15_03-yu007.m4a",
      "text": "お題は、「『根性』に言葉を足して可愛くして下さい」\nうちの回答は……『ベビー根性焼き』！",
      "startTime": 70.0650158265,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_laugh-01.m4a",
          "delay": 4568.315901600002,
          "startTime": 74.6333317281
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_talkstudio-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "talkstudio-00-noon",
      "startTime": 74.6333317281
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_15_03/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_15_03-koh004.m4a",
      "text": "（おぉ……かなりの高得点だ。会場のウケもいい）\n（回答のタイミングもいいし、順調に勝ち進んでいるな）",
      "startTime": 78.7333350342,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_talkstudio-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "talkstudio-00-noon",
      "startTime": 88.5666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_15_03/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_15_03-yu008.m4a",
      "text": "次は「このアイドル、京都人だな。なぜ分かった？」\nまんまうちのことやないかーい！",
      "startTime": 88.7666683675,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_talkstudio-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "talkstudio-00-noon",
      "startTime": 91.2666650614
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_15_03/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_15_03-yu009.m4a",
      "text": "はい！　『アンコールでぶぶ漬けを配り始めた』\n……うちはやったことありませんからね？",
      "startTime": 96.2666683675,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_laugh-01.m4a",
          "delay": 2266.664965800004,
          "startTime": 98.5333333333
        },
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_laugh-01.m4a",
          "delay": 2499.9982990999997,
          "startTime": 98.7666666666
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_15_03/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_15_03-koh005.m4a",
      "text": "（おぉ、今までで一番会場が沸いたぞ）\n（お題も優にぴったりだったし、これなら……）",
      "startTime": 103.0333350342,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_talkstudio-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "talkstudio-00-noon",
      "startTime": 106.6333383403
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_15_03/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_15_03-koh006.m4a",
      "text": "（優、もしかして、本当に優勝してしまうのか？）\n（そうしたら、お笑い事務所からのスカウトが……？）",
      "startTime": 111.4000017008,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": null,
      "speakerName": "",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "――決勝戦、最後の問題",
      "startTime": 116.0000095847,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_talkstudio-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "talkstudio-00-noon",
      "startTime": 117.4666747255
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_15_03/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_15_03-yu010.m4a",
      "text": "次はいよいよ最後の問題……\n「最新の冷蔵庫、この機能いらんやろ。どんな機能？」",
      "startTime": 121.4333350342,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_15_03/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_15_03-koh007.m4a",
      "text": "（こ、これは……練習で優がスベったお題じゃないか）\n（でも、今の優ならきっと大丈夫だ。信じてるぞ）",
      "startTime": 131.9333350342,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_talkstudio-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "talkstudio-00-noon",
      "startTime": 136.4333459698
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_15_03/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_15_03-yu011.m4a",
      "text": "こ、これは……！　でも、今のうちは\nあの時だだスベりしたうちやない！　……はい！",
      "startTime": 141.0000017008,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_talkstudio-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "talkstudio-00-noon",
      "startTime": 145.8333520733
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_talkstudio-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "talkstudio-00-noon",
      "startTime": 150.3666683675
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_15_03/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_15_03-yu012.m4a",
      "text": "うちの回答はこれです！　『ブルーライトカット』！\nなんで冷蔵庫にブルーライトカット？　いらんやろ！",
      "startTime": 150.3666683675,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_lesson-01-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "lesson-01-000-noon",
      "startTime": 155.35001874
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_15_03/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_15_03-yu013.m4a",
      "text": "うちの答えは……『浴室乾燥機能』！\nなんで冷蔵庫に浴室乾燥機能？　いらんやろ！",
      "startTime": 161.0333350342,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_talkstudio-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "talkstudio-00-noon",
      "startTime": 166.150026878
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_talkstudio-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "talkstudio-00-noon",
      "startTime": 166.150026878
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_15_03/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_15_03-koh008.m4a",
      "text": "（……いや、なんでそこだけ成長してないんだ？）\n（それとも、そこだけは譲れなかったのか……優……）",
      "startTime": 170.2000017008,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_talkstudio-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "talkstudio-00-noon",
      "startTime": 174.5333602114
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_15_03/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_15_03-yu014.m4a",
      "text": "……え？　あれ？　そんな、うち……\n決勝の、最後の最後で……だだスベりしてもうた！？",
      "startTime": 180.6666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_talkstudio-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "talkstudio-00-noon",
      "startTime": 183.6666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_talkstudio-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "talkstudio-00-noon",
      "startTime": 187.1666631063
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_15_03/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_15_03-koh009.m4a",
      "text": "（このだだスベりが響いて、優は優勝を逃してしまった）\n（続いて、アフタートークの収録が始まる）",
      "startTime": 193.0999966146,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_talkstudio-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "talkstudio-00-noon",
      "startTime": 196.1333480044
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_15_03/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_15_03-yu015.m4a",
      "text": "惜しくも優勝は逃しましたね、って……\nも～勘弁して下さい！　うち、まだ傷心中なんですから",
      "startTime": 200.4333299479,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_laugh-01.m4a",
          "delay": 16466.6700521,
          "startTime": 216.9
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_talkstudio-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "talkstudio-00-noon",
      "startTime": 206.700014671
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_15_03/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_15_03-yu016.m4a",
      "text": "え？　でも爪痕は残せた？　ありがとうございます\nうちの心にも深～い傷痕が残ってますけどね！",
      "startTime": 213.2666632813,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_talkstudio-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "talkstudio-00-noon",
      "startTime": 218.4333490216
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_15_03/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_15_03-yu017.m4a",
      "text": "優勝出来んかったの、ほんま悔しいです\nいつかリベンジしますから、絶対また呼んで下さいね！",
      "startTime": 222.7000057699,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_talkstudio-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "talkstudio-00-noon",
      "startTime": 227.066682355
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_15_03/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_15_03-koh010.m4a",
      "text": "（優勝は逃がしたが、快進撃からのだだスベりが効いて）\n（審査員の方々が、いい感じに優をいじってくれたな）",
      "startTime": 231.1000057699,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_15_03/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_15_03-koh011.m4a",
      "text": "（お陰でいい空気が出来上がっている。今告知したら）\n（……もしかして、優勝した以上に目立つんじゃないか？）",
      "startTime": 240.2000057699,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_talkstudio-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "talkstudio-00-noon",
      "startTime": 244.366682355
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_15_03/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_15_03-yu018.m4a",
      "text": "名だたる芸人のみなさんに並んで、この番組に出られて\nいい刺激をいただきました。ありがとうございました！",
      "startTime": 248.6666724366,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_laugh-01.m4a",
          "delay": 10033.336718699986,
          "startTime": 258.7000091553
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_talkstudio-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "talkstudio-00-noon",
      "startTime": 253.0333490216
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_15_03/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_15_03-yu019.m4a",
      "text": "え？　「褒めても告知の時間は十秒しか延びない」？\nって、延びるんかーい！　ふふ、破格ですね。ほな――",
      "startTime": 257.9666724366,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_15_03/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_15_03-yu020.m4a",
      "text": "今日うちが着てる衣装は、今度トリエル全員で出演する\nミュージカル、『空の宝石』の衣装なんです",
      "startTime": 270.7666724366,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_15_03/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_15_03-yu021.m4a",
      "text": "宝石の体と永遠の命を持つ種族の国\nそのお姫様役に、すみれちゃんと一緒に挑戦します",
      "startTime": 279.4333452067,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_15_03/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_15_03-yu022.m4a",
      "text": "そして瑠依ちゃんは、そんなうちらの国に\n迷い込んできた、人間の少女の役を担当します",
      "startTime": 286.9666988851,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_15_03/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_15_03-yu023.m4a",
      "text": "面白いのはもちろんですけど、生きるとは何か\n人生の輝きとは何か……考えさせられる内容なんです",
      "startTime": 295.8667110921,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_15_03/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_15_03-yu024.m4a",
      "text": "お笑いとはちょーっと方向性が違いますけど\n観に来てくれたみなさんを、物語の中へと誘います",
      "startTime": 305.3333899658,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_15_03/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_15_03-yu025.m4a",
      "text": "笑いとはまた違った感動で、心を揺さぶってみせます\nミュージカルも観てもらえたら嬉しいです！",
      "startTime": 314.7666968505,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_talkstudio-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "talkstudio-00-noon",
      "startTime": 318.6333470661
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_talkstudio-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "talkstudio-00-noon",
      "startTime": 325.0000139077
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_15_03/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_15_03-yu026.m4a",
      "text": "……少し時間が余ったので、自分のことをお話しします\nうち、人生は挑戦し続けることで輝く、と思ってます",
      "startTime": 325.0000139077,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_talkstudio-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "talkstudio-00-noon",
      "startTime": 330.7666762513
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_15_03/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_15_03-yu027.m4a",
      "text": "お笑いも、まだまだ不慣れですけど\n一生懸命練習して、今日という日に臨みました",
      "startTime": 334.2666805744,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_talkstudio-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "talkstudio-00-noon",
      "startTime": 339.2333429179
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_15_03/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_15_03-yu028.m4a",
      "text": "優勝は逃しましたけど、みなさんに沢山笑ってもらえて\n心の底から、やって良かったと思ってます",
      "startTime": 344.4000139077,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_talkstudio-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "talkstudio-00-noon",
      "startTime": 348.3666762513
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_15_03/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_15_03-koh012.m4a",
      "text": "（優の、トリエルの挑戦、か。挑戦を重ねるごとに）\n（彼女達の輝きは、鮮やかさを増していくな）",
      "startTime": 354.4000139077,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_talkstudio-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "talkstudio-00-noon",
      "startTime": 357.8000095846
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_15_03/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_15_03-yu029.m4a",
      "text": "うちはこれからも頂点目指して頑張ります\nそう、お笑い界の、頂点を目指して……！",
      "startTime": 361.9000139077,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_15_03/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_15_03-koh013.m4a",
      "text": "（……そっちじゃないだろ！？）",
      "startTime": 365.9000095846,
      "sfxList": []
